name: Air Fryer Tater Tots®
author: Soup Loving Nicole
summary: This simple, how-to recipe is perfect for those cooking for few people. You can cook without ever heating up your oven and the result is perfectly crispy tots. Temperature and time are the same regardless of servings. Easy peasy.
ingredients: 36  frozen bite-size potato nuggets (such as Tater Tots®)
directions: Preheat an air fryer to 350 degrees F (175 degrees C) for 4 minutes
Place desired amount of potato nuggets into the air fryer basket in a single layer, working in batches if necessary
Cook in the preheated air fryer for 6 minutes
Cook until crispy, or to desired doneness, about 4 minutes more
